Please complete the following scenarios, in either ruby, javascript, or both.

- A deck should be able to be shuffled
- A 5-card poker hand should be dealt to 3 players
- A hand should be valued (e.g. a pair, 2 pair, 3 pair)
- A winning hand should be selected from the 3 players

- The ranks of hands are:
  ----------------------
  Ace high
  Pair
  2 Pair
  3 of a kind
  straight ( 5 in order )
  flush ( same suit )
  full house ( 3 of a kind, and a pair )
  4 of a kind
  straight flush

- Bonus points for a texas holdem implementation

Please fork the repository, and email us at developers@watermelonexpress.com when you are finished.
